===Throwable Potions (Exclusive to Oakveil Woodlands)===
* {{ItemFrame|Beauty Elixir|type=Buff}} - Polymorphs all targets in the area into Sheep. Is required to end '''Lucile's''' "'''Alchemic Madness'''" state.
* {{ItemFrame|Liquid Fire|type=Buff}} - Sets the area and all targets entering it on fire. The burn makes Gold Golems vulnerable to attacks for the duration. Instantly kills [[Corrupted Mantrap]].
* {{ItemFrame|Pixies Luck|type=Buff}} - Dramatically increases player movement speed.
* {{ItemFrame|Potion of Dispel|type=Buff}} - Knocks targets back and dispels all effects on targets hit, including '''Lucile's''' "'''Gold Skin'''" invulnerability.
* {{ItemFrame|Rejuvenation Juice|type=Buff}} - Applies a healing buff to targets in the area. Taking damage ends the effect.
